ECMAScript Language Binding


This appendix contains the complete ECMAScript  binding for the Level 2 Document Object Model Style
  definitions. The definitions are divided into 
    StyleSheets and
    CSS.




	  Exceptions handling is only supported by ECMAScript implementation
	  conformant with the Standard ECMA-262 3rd. Edition ().





